INSTALL UNDER UNIX

  You need the OCaml compilers installed to compile. They must be
  accessible in the path.

  Do:
     ./configure
     make
  Optionnally, do:
     make bootstrap
  Optionnally do:
     make opt
     make opt.opt
  Become root and do:
     make install

INSTALL UNDER WINDOWS

  Under Windows, you need the Cygwin environment. The above directives
  apply.
